Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電視上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.82,0:00:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在播放著相同的畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:11.00,up,NTP,0,0,0,,目前  依然無法與新拜科努爾基地取得聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:15.16,up,NTP,0,0,0,,事故原因等具體消息依然尚不明瞭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事故發生後已經過去了半天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特的媽媽依然是生死不明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據衛星拍攝的畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整個新拜科努爾基地都受到了爆炸的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前火勢依舊兇猛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外  搭載在火箭上的實驗堆也有可能發生了爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.59,0:02:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不排除有洩漏的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說情況更加惡化了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然沒有倖存者的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣  不僅僅是火箭爆炸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼  會發生這種事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡是發生一些讓我們束手無策的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論什麼事情都是有可能發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到真的發生  沒人能料到會發生怎樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經發生了的事情  是必定會發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能被悲慘的現實擊垮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要堅信自己必能克服這樣的悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小庫…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全部都想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在牢房…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牢房？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜下來  庫特莉亞芙卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的哦  小庫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都陪著你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天深夜  庫特回了宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特沒來上課
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們除了擔心  無計可施
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搭載在火箭上的實驗堆爆炸了的可能性非常高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由於擔心存在洩漏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後可能將暫時關閉圖布亞的邊境
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說因為圖布亞現在處在危險之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是進入還是離開圖布亞都變得非常困難了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火箭裡的機組人員是生是死  依然沒有消息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小庫她擔心媽媽的安危  一定正坐立不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定  非常想飛回圖布亞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  現在無法進入圖布亞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圖布亞大使館給了庫特莉亞芙卡回國的機票
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子的母親  在圖布亞似乎是個非常有名的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此特許她的女兒回國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:05:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是讓她回去確認母親是否平安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說明天  大使館的人就會來接那孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼庫特她  要回圖布亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在那裡太危險了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能去了就再也回不來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  小庫應該很想見自己媽媽的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小庫的媽媽也一定安然無恙  正等著女兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴你也這麼覺得的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的媽媽  已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定也只會留下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悲傷的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是別回去好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷心的事情可怕的事情還是別看的好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特她太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good Morning  錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good Afternoon  不對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特  不用在意這個的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓大家擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起大家  現在庫特和庫特的媽媽才是更重要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你收到機票了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特你準備回圖布亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想見媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我卻不能回圖布亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我來這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來日本…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是逃過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃過來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能聽我說說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻傻的我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從小就非常憧憬媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒跟別人說起過  我的夢想就是成為Cosmonaut
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫妮雅  你剛才說了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成為Cosmonaut  你是這麼說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然也立志當太空人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讓人高興死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特莉亞芙卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特莉亞芙卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為替你取了這個名字而感到自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一個進入宇宙的萊卡犬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小的生命裡蘊含著人類未來大大的希望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特莉亞芙卡成為了這個世界裡至關重要的一顆齒輪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就和你的名字一樣  成為世界裡的一顆齒輪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有益於世界的一顆齒輪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣在一年前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我進入了圖布亞的航空學校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航空學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是訓練Cosmonaut的專業機構
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為了實現自己的夢想  發奮學習
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是比起預想  現實並沒有那麼順利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在宇宙裡必須會說英語和俄語
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為上課用的是英語
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力就有回報什麼的  根本就沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.69,0:08:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明媽媽那麼天賦異稟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女兒卻是個廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經常被嘲笑我這是在浪費國家的預算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都覺得我滑稽可笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼努力  依然是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得自己不是媽媽的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果只在學校待了半年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與媽媽不辭而別  我逃到了日本來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而在這裡  我還是沒什麼出息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼也不算  什麼都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個對世界沒用的廢物齒輪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知媽媽對這麼軟弱的我會有多失望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不能回圖布亞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特的軟弱不是人皆有之的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴就像在聽自己的故事般  一直低著頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特公還在猶豫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人你怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種複雜的事情我怎麼會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹  你多想想嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是最擅長思考了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得庫特還是回去比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定很擔心她媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是庫特還沒能整理好自己的思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果現在不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能美女士肯定會後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許這輩子都見不到母親了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特莉亞芙卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起沒去而後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是去了之後再後悔更好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不向前進  就得不到任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須得去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想留在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在大家的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會去給大使館打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把機票還給他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是庫特做的決定  我們沒資格去說三道四
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說飛起來  甚至連前進都做不到的庫特莉亞芙卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你似乎已經想起所有事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又打算重複同樣的時間  同樣的經歷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能美你的願望改變了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論能美你做什麼選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹以及我們都不會責怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  恭介同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介也認為庫特應該回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對他人說「去勇敢面對痛苦」是很簡單的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說說是很容易的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我沒有堅強到能對庫特說出這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論選擇什麼  最後剩下的只有後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂的正確答案  根本不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杉並同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  修學旅行馬上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一點都高興不起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三枝同學也肯定是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在活動室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.15,0:14:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴  你肌肉不夠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呆站著幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要準備燒掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  這是值日生的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微…等下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用確認一下裡面的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是不可燃垃圾就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊  有可能是食物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是在庫特房間裡見過的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是庫特扔的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:40.06,up,NTP,0,0,0,,這個真帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:43.65,up,NTP,0,0,0,,但是對肌肉好像沒啥用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:45.35,up,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒法吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼零件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:14:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是身份識別牌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄語
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫公打算把這麼重要的東西燒掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個箱子可以先放在我這兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙開發史
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二次世界大戰後  最先發射人造衛星的是蘇維埃聯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘坐斯普特尼克飛上宇宙的13隻狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,чернушка
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英語是Blacky
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特的媽媽是黑頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是她媽媽的身份識別牌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙工學概論
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德維特和艾弗雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.31,0:15:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖埃克蘇佩里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星之王子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個箱子裡  滿載著庫特的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我證明了一下為什麼天空是藍的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好感動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾弗雷特的宇宙平行理論如果是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼這個世界上就會有無數個南十字星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直美妙到我快昏過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚我寫了一篇關於黑洞和相對論的小論文
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為很難為情  所以沒有告訴任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你入學  庫妮雅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是媽媽進入宇航局後一直在穿的披風和帽子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望它們能替我永遠保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個帽子和披風
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你媽媽的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此重要的箱子  真的要丟掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我夢想的殘骸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後悔的集合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經沒有資格擁有它了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不適合做什麼Cosmonaut
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.55,0:17:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論怎樣逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特都沒法抹消自己心中真正的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的想法？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特發自心底…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憧憬著宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必非要做到像你媽媽那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算很稚嫩  很笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特只要尋找到自己力所能及的事情就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特只要做個像庫特的齒輪  追逐宇宙之夢就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你憧憬的媽媽傳達給你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特很想見媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能逃避這種想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便被說成是膽小鬼又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為庫特最喜歡自己的媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會再逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想見媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要去見她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我想要去見她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這大概也是我想對自己說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「不能逃避」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你的說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機票帶了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要小心點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特萊爾卡  威爾卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特萊爾卡和威爾卡能拜託你照顧一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.99,0:19:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:19:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要聽鈴同學的話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大使館的人說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我或許回不來日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約好了  一定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們等著你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來是能美…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是只有能美才能辦到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mission哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我經常在媽媽面前勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其實那並不是真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論在何處  都會被人嘲笑成怪孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我總是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但現在有了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家接受了真實的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:20:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.06,0:21:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請念出「ни пуха ни пера」這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是祈求幸運的咒語哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泥噗喀…泥呸啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.09,0:21:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見  小庫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等著你哦  能美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Прощайте
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面對著重重困難
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特獨自啟程了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  一定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圖布亞的情況超乎預想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到祖國的庫特迎來了荒謬的試煉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.73,0:23:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只能祈禱她的平安嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.55,0:23:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特危在旦夕
